        "summary": "Pan-roasted East Coast Skate, Anchovy And Broccoli Pickle is a hor d'oeuvre that serves 2. One serving contains <b>465 calories</b>, <b>2g of protein</b>, and <b>49g of fat</b>. For <b>$1.93 per serving</b>, this recipe <b>covers 6%</b> of your daily requirements of vitamins and minerals. From preparation to the plate, this recipe takes approximately <b>8 minutes</b>. A mixture of maldon sea salt and freshly cracked pepper, sherry vinegar, juice of lime, and a handful of other ingredients are all it takes to make this recipe so yummy. It is brought to you by The British Larder. 1 person were impressed by this recipe. It is a good option if you're following a <b>gluten free and pescatarian</b> diet. All things considered, we decided this recipe <b>deserves a spoonacular score of 20%</b>. This score is rather bad. If you like this recipe, you might also like recipes such as <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/pan-roasted-salmon-with-purple-sprouting-broccoli-and-anchovy-r-450\">Pan-roasted Salmon With Purple Sprouting Broccoli And Anchovy-r</a>, <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/skate-chicory-and-anchovy-29\">Skate, Chicory, and Anchovy</a>, and <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/east-coast-tomato-soup-425079\">East Coast Tomato Soup</a>.",
