        "image": "https://spoonacular.com/recipeImages/34-556x370.jpg",
        "imageType": "jpg",
        "summary": "Need a <b>gluten free, primal, and pescatarian side dish</b>? Cardoons With Anchovy-garlic Sauce could be an awesome recipe to try. This recipe serves 6. For <b>65 cents per serving</b>, this recipe <b>covers 3%</b> of your daily requirements of vitamins and minerals. One serving contains <b>210 calories</b>, <b>2g of protein</b>, and <b>22g of fat</b>. 3 people have made this recipe and would make it again. If you have oil-packed anchovy filets, butter, olive oil, and a few other ingredients on hand, you can make it. It is brought to you by Saveur. From preparation to the plate, this recipe takes approximately <b>45 minutes</b>. With a spoonacular <b>score of 20%</b>, this dish is not so amazing. Try <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/pappardelle-with-tomato-garlic-and-anchovy-sauce-365697\">Pappardelle with Tomato, Garlic and Anchovy Sauce</a>, <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/pasta-with-15-minute-garlic-oil-and-anchovy-sauce-873114\">Pasta With 15-Minute Garlic, Oil, and Anchovy Sauce</a>, and <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/peppers-with-garlic-anchovy-sauce-peperoni-con-bagna-cauda-598793\">Peppers with Garlic-Anchovy Sauce | Peperoni con Bagna Cauda</a> for similar recipes.",
